 } } \right),$$<br><br>$${C^3} = \left( {\matrix{
   0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0  \cr 
   0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0  \cr 
   0 &amp; 0 &amp; 0  \cr 

 } } \right) = {C^4} = {C^5} = ........$$<br><br>$$B = 7{A^{20}} - 20{A^7} + 2I$$<br><br>$$ = 7{(I + C)^{20}} + 20{(I + C)^7} + 2I$$<br><br>$$ = 7(I + 20C + {}^{20}{C_2}{C^2}) - 20(I + 7C + {}^7{C_2}{C^2}) + 2I$$<br><br> So<br><br>$${b_{13}} = 7 \times {}^{20}{C_2}{C^2} - 20 \times {}^7{C_2} = 910$$

